<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SVS — Report Emergency</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --amber:        #FACC15;
      --amber-dark:   #EAB308;
      --amber-deep:   #CA8A04;
      --amber-light:  #FEFCE8;
      --amber-border: #FDE047;
      --orange:       #DC2626;
      --orange-light: #FEF2F2;
      --orange-border:#FCA5A5;
      --red:          #DC2626;
      --red-light:    #FEF2F2;
      --red-border:   #FCA5A5;
      --green:        #2563EB;
      --green-light:  #DBEAFE;
      --green-border: #93C5FD;
      --blue:         #1D4ED8;
      --page-bg:      #e9f0ff;
      --page-bg2:     #fff7ef;
      --bg:           #f5f7ff;
      --surface:      #F4F8FF;
      --border:       #BFD6F5;
      --border-mid:   #97BDE9;
      --text:         #0F172A;
      --text2:        #1E3A8A;
      --muted:        #334155;
      --muted2:       #64748B;
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,.08),0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,.05);
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 14px rgba(15,23,42,.10),0 2px 6px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
      --shadow-lg: 0 12px 36px rgba(15,23,42,.12),0 4px 14px rgba(15,23,42,.07);
      --shadow-xl: 0 24px 56px rgba(15,23,42,.14),0 8px 20px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
      --r-sm:8px; --r-md:12px; --r-lg:16px; --r-xl:20px;
    }
    *,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
    body{
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;color:var(--text);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;line-height:1.65;
      background:
        radial-gradient(520px 360px at 120% -20%, rgba(59,130,246,.16), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(420px 280px at -10% 120%, rgba(239,68,68,.12), transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f2f6ff 0%, #fff7ef 82%, #ffffff 100%);
    }
    a{color:var(--blue);text-decoration:none;}
    a:visited{color:var(--blue);}
    a:hover{color:#0f3fb5;}
    ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;} ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg);} ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border-mid);border-radius:99px;}

    header{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:1rem;padding:1rem 1.5rem;background:rgba(243,247,255,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08);color:var(--text);}
    .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.6rem;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none;}
    .brand img{width:72px;height:60px;object-fit:contain;flex-shrink:0;}
    .brand-text{line-height:1;}
    .brand-name{font-weight:900;font-size:1.25rem;letter-spacing:-.2px;color:var(--text);}
    .brand-sub{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:#475569;}
    .header-right{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;width:100%;justify-items:center;}
    .nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.65rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;}
    .nav-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:.5rem 1.1rem;border:1.6px solid rgba(151,189,233,.9);border-radius:15px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff,#f3f7ff);color:var(--text);font-weight:820;font-size:.9rem;transition:.16s;box-shadow:0 9px 18px rgba(15,23,42,.08);}
    .nav-btn:hover{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--blue);box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(29,78,216,.15);}
    .nav-btn.active{border-color:var(--blue);background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f0f5ff,#dfe9ff);color:var(--blue);box-shadow:0 12px 26px rgba(29,78,216,.22);}
    .nav-btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--blue);outline-offset:2px;}
    .nav-btn svg{width:14px;height:14px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .main-datetime{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;min-height:56px;padding:.65rem 1rem;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#ffffff,#eef3ff) padding-box,linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(239,68,68,.9),rgba(59,130,246,.9)) border-box;border:1.6px solid transparent;border-radius:18px;color:#0F172A;white-space:nowrap;box-shadow:0 14px 26px rgba(0,0,0,.08), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.65);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);}
    .main-datetime:hover{
      transform:translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow:0 16px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.12), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.8);
    }
    .main-datetime svg{width:22px;height:18px;stroke:var(--blue);fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;flex-shrink:0;}
    .time-block{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.05;min-width:0;}
    .clock-text{font-family:'Orbitron','JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.08rem;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.1px;color:#0b1a3a;}
    .date-text{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.8px;color:#4b5563;margin-top:3px;}
    .sos-save-row{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.55rem;flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top:.4rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:.55rem .75rem;
    }
    .sos-save-row label{font-weight:800;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text2);}
    .sos-save-row input{
      width:180px;max-width:220px;
      padding:.55rem .75rem;border-radius:10px;border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);
      font-weight:700;font-size:.92rem;
    }
    .sos-save-row button{
      border:1.5px solid var(--blue);background:var(--blue);color:#fff;
      padding:.5rem .9rem;border-radius:10px;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .sos-save-row button:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);}
    .sos-save-row .pill-status{font-weight:700;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);}

    /* ── PANIC STRIP ── */
    .panic-strip{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#E9F2FF 0%,#FEFCE8 52%,#FEF2F2 100%);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(220,38,38,.12);
      padding:2.5rem 1.5rem 2.75rem;
      text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .panic-strip::before{
      content:'';position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;
      transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
      width:420px;height:420px;border-radius:50%;
      background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(29,78,216,.12) 0%,transparent 68%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .panic-eyebrow{
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);
      margin-bottom:1.4rem;position:relative;
    }
    .panic-btn{
      width:168px;height:168px;border-radius:50%;
      background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF4444,#DC2626,#B91C1C);
      border:none;cursor:pointer;
      margin:0 auto 1.6rem;
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:9px;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 12px rgba(220,38,38,.09),0 0 0 24px rgba(220,38,38,.05),0 10px 40px rgba(220,38,38,.38);
      transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s;
      animation:panicPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      position:relative;
    }
    @keyframes panicPulse{
      0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 12px rgba(220,38,38,.09),0 0 0 24px rgba(220,38,38,.05),0 10px 40px rgba(220,38,38,.38);}
      50%{box-shadow:0 0 0 18px rgba(220,38,38,.12),0 0 0 34px rgba(220,38,38,.06),0 14px 52px rgba(220,38,38,.46);}
    }
    .panic-btn:active{transform:scale(.93);animation:none;}
    .panic-btn svg{width:44px;height:44px;stroke:#fff;stroke-width:1.6;fill:none;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .panic-btn-label{font-weight:900;font-size:.8rem;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.95);}
    .panic-sublabel{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--text2);max-width:290px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.65;position:relative;}
    .panic-sublabel strong{color:var(--text);}
    .panic-number-pill{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
      background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border-mid);
      border-radius:99px;padding:.35rem 1rem;
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--muted);
      margin-top:.85rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;
    }
    .panic-number-pill:hover{border-color:var(--red);color:var(--red);}
    .panic-number-pill svg{width:13px;height:13px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .panic-number-pill strong{color:var(--green);}

    /* ── FORM ── */
    .form-wrap{max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;padding:2.75rem 1.5rem 5rem;position:relative;z-index:1;}

    .form-head{margin-bottom:2.5rem;animation:fadeUp .5s ease both;}
    @keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
    .form-eyebrow{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.6rem;font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);
      background:var(--red-light);border:1px solid var(--red-border);
      border-radius:99px;padding:.28rem .85rem;margin-bottom:.9rem;
    }
    .form-eyebrow svg{width:12px;height:12px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .form-head h1{font-weight:900;font-size:2.9rem;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-2px;}
    .form-head h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--red);position:relative;}
    .form-head h1 em::after{
      content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-3px;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red),var(--orange));
      border-radius:2px;opacity:.55;
    }
    .form-head p{margin-top:1rem;color:var(--text2);font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7;max-width:500px;}
    .head-actions{display:flex;gap:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:.8rem;}
    .chip-btn{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:.45rem .8rem;
      border-radius:999px;border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);background:#fff;
      color:var(--text2);font-weight:800;font-size:.8rem;cursor:pointer;
      transition:all .18s;box-shadow:var(--shadow-xs);
    }
    .chip-btn:hover{border-color:var(--amber-border);background:var(--amber-light);color:var(--amber-deep);}
    .chip-btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--red),#ef4444);border-color:transparent;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(220,38,38,.2);}
    .chip-btn.primary:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(220,38,38,.26);transform:translateY(-1px);}

    .alert-strip{
      display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.85rem;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FEFCE8,#FEF2F2);border:1px solid var(--orange-border);
      border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:1.05rem 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom:2.25rem;font-size:.87rem;line-height:1.65;
      animation:fadeUp .4s .08s ease both;
    }
    .alert-strip svg{width:18px;height:18px;stroke:var(--orange);fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
    .alert-strip strong{color:var(--orange);}
    .alert-strip span{color:var(--text2);}

    /* cards */
    .card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#F8FBFF,#EEF5FF);border:1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:var(--r-xl);padding:2rem;
      margin-bottom:1.25rem;
      box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
      transition:box-shadow .22s,border-color .22s,transform .22s;
      position:relative;overflow:hidden;
      animation:fadeUp .5s ease both;
    }
    .card::before{
      content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--amber),var(--orange),transparent);
      opacity:0;transition:opacity .22s;border-radius:var(--r-xl) var(--r-xl) 0 0;
    }
    .card:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);border-color:var(--border-mid);transform:translateY(-2px);}
    .card:hover::before{opacity:1;}
    .card:nth-child(1){animation-delay:.07s;}
    .card:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.14s;}
    .card:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.21s;}
    .card:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.28s;}
    .card:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.35s;}

    .card-head{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;margin-bottom:1.6rem;}
    .card-icon{
      width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:11px;flex-shrink:0;
      background:var(--amber-light);border:1.5px solid var(--amber-border);
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    }
    .card-icon svg{width:22px;height:22px;stroke:var(--amber-deep);fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .card-step{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.58rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3px;}
    .card-title{font-weight:820;font-size:1.08rem;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:-.25px;}
    .card-sub{font-size:.77rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;}

    .row2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;}
    @media(max-width:520px){.row2{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
    .field{margin-bottom:1rem;}
    .field:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
    .field label{display:block;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:.45rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;}
    .input-wrap{position:relative;}
    .input-wrap svg.field-icon{
      position:absolute;left:11px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);
      width:15px;height:15px;stroke:var(--muted2);fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .input-wrap.has-icon input,
    .input-wrap.has-icon select{padding-left:2.35rem;}
    .attest-check{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.65rem;
      font-weight:800;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text2);
      cursor:pointer;user-select:none;
    }
    .attest-check input{
      width:18px;height:18px;min-width:18px;
      accent-color:var(--red);
      cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;
      appearance:checkbox;
      padding:0;margin:0;
      box-shadow:none;border:none;background:transparent;
    }
    .attest-check span{line-height:1.4;}
    input,select,textarea{
      width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--text);padding:.78rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--r-md);
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:.92rem;font-weight:500;
      transition:border-color .18s,box-shadow .18s,background .18s;
      outline:none;appearance:none;
    }
    input:focus,select:focus,textarea:focus{
      border-color:var(--amber);background:var(--surface);
      box-shadow:0 0 0 3.5px rgba(245,158,11,.13);
    }
    input::placeholder,textarea::placeholder{color:var(--muted2);font-weight:400;}
    textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:115px;}
    select option{background:#fff;}
    .req-missing{
      border-color:var(--red)!important;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 3.5px rgba(220,38,38,.2)!important;
      animation:reqPulse 1.1s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .etype-grid.req-missing .etype-btn,
    .sev-row.req-missing .sev-btn{
      border-color:var(--red)!important;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(220,38,38,.13);
    }
    .gps-btn.req-missing{
      border-style:solid;
      border-color:var(--red)!important;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 3.5px rgba(220,38,38,.2)!important;
      color:var(--red);
    }
    @keyframes reqPulse{
      0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 3.5px rgba(220,38,38,.2);}
      50%{box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(220,38,38,.1);}
    }

    /* emergency type grid */
    .etype-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:.85rem;}
    @media(max-width:440px){.etype-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
    .etype-btn{
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:9px;
      padding:1.3rem .6rem 1.05rem;
      border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:13px;
      background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);
      cursor:pointer;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.82rem;
      transition:all .2s;
    }
    .etype-icon{
      width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:11px;
      background:#F0F6FF;border:1.5px solid var(--border);
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      transition:all .2s;
    }
    .etype-icon svg{width:20px;height:20px;stroke:var(--muted);fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;transition:stroke .2s;}
    .etype-btn:hover,.etype-btn.sel{
      border-color:var(--amber);background:var(--amber-light);
      color:var(--amber-deep);transform:translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(245,158,11,.18);
    }
    .etype-btn:hover .etype-icon,.etype-btn.sel .etype-icon{background:var(--amber-light);border-color:var(--amber-border);}
    .etype-btn:hover .etype-icon svg,.etype-btn.sel .etype-icon svg{stroke:var(--amber-deep);}
    .etype-btn:hover .etype-copy strong,.etype-btn.sel .etype-copy strong{color:var(--amber-deep);}

    /* severity */
    .sev-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:.85rem;}
    .sev-btn{
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:7px;
      padding:.9rem;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:11px;
      background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);
      cursor:pointer;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;
      transition:all .2s;
    }
    .sev-btn svg{width:17px;height:17px;fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;transition:stroke .2s;}
    .sev-btn.low{border-color:rgba(16,185,129,.18);background:rgba(236,253,245,.6);color:#0f766e;}
    .sev-btn.med{border-color:rgba(245,158,11,.22);background:rgba(255,251,235,.65);color:#b45309;}
    .sev-btn.high{border-color:rgba(239,68,68,.22);background:rgba(254,242,242,.65);color:#b91c1c;}
    .sev-btn.low:hover,.sev-btn.low.sel   {background:var(--green-light);border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(5,150,105,.14);}
    .sev-btn.low:hover svg,.sev-btn.low.sel svg{stroke:var(--green);}
    .sev-btn.med:hover,.sev-btn.med.sel   {background:var(--amber-light);border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber-dark);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(245,158,11,.14);}
    .sev-btn.med:hover svg,.sev-btn.med.sel svg{stroke:var(--amber-dark);}
    .sev-btn.high:hover,.sev-btn.high.sel {background:var(--red-light);border-color:var(--red);color:var(--red);transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(220,38,38,.14);}
    .sev-btn.high:hover svg,.sev-btn.high.sel svg{stroke:var(--red);}

    /* tags */
    .tag-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:.55rem;}
    .tag-chip{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
      padding:.48rem .78rem;border-radius:999px;
      border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);
      background:#fff;color:var(--text2);font-weight:750;font-size:.8rem;
      cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;box-shadow:var(--shadow-xs);
    }
    .tag-chip:hover{border-color:var(--amber-border);background:var(--amber-light);color:var(--amber-deep);}
    .tag-chip.sel{border-color:var(--blue);background:var(--blue-light);color:var(--blue);}
    .tag-chip svg{width:14px;height:14px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;}

    /* gps btn */
    .gps-btn{
      width:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;
      padding:.88rem;border:1.5px dashed var(--border-mid);border-radius:var(--r-md);
      background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:.88rem;font-weight:600;
      cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;margin-bottom:1rem;
    }
    .gps-btn svg{width:16px;height:16px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .gps-btn:hover{border-style:solid;border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber-dark);background:var(--amber-light);}
    .gps-btn.got{border-style:solid;border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green);background:var(--green-light);}
    .gps-map-wrap{
      display:none;
      margin:-.2rem 0 1rem;
      border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);
      border-radius:12px;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:var(--surface);
      position:relative;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .gps-map-head{
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:.65rem;
      padding:.55rem .75rem;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
      background:var(--surface2);
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
      font-size:.62rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.7px;color:var(--muted);
      text-transform:uppercase;
      z-index:2;
    }
    .gps-map-head a{
      color:var(--amber-dark);
      text-decoration:none;
      font-weight:700;
    }
    .gps-map-head a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
    .gps-map-canvas{
      position:relative;
      width:100%;
      background:#EEF2FF;
      border-radius:0 0 10px 10px;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .gps-map-frame{
      width:100%;
      height:260px;
      border:0;
      display:block;
      background:#F3F4F6;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }
    .gps-map-view-toggle{
      position:absolute;
      top:12px;
      left:12px;
      z-index:3;
    }
    .gps-map-zoom{
      position:absolute;
      top:12px;
      right:12px;
      z-index:3;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:.4rem;
      padding:4px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.9);
      border:1px solid rgba(15,23,42,.1);
      box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(15,23,42,.18);
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
      font-size:.68rem;
      letter-spacing:.6px;
      color:var(--muted2);
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }
    .gps-map-control{
      border:1px solid transparent;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.95);
      color:var(--text2);
      font-weight:700;
      padding:.35rem .9rem;
      font-size:.78rem;
      cursor:pointer;
      box-shadow:0 4px 18px rgba(15,23,42,.2);
      transition:all .2s;
    }
    .gps-map-control--compact{
      width:34px;
      height:34px;
      padding:0;
      font-size:1.25rem;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      box-shadow:none;
    }
    .gps-map-control:hover:not(:disabled){
      border-color:var(--border-mid);
      transform:translateY(-1px);
    }
    .gps-map-control.active{
      border-color:var(--blue);
      color:var(--blue);
      background:rgba(59,130,246,.12);
    }
    .gps-map-control:disabled{
      opacity:.5;
      cursor:not-allowed;
    }
    .gps-map-zoom span{
      min-width:44px;
      text-align:center;
      font-size:.85rem;
      font-weight:700;
      color:var(--text2);
    }

    /* upload */
    .upload-area{
      position:relative;border:2px dashed var(--border-mid);border-radius:13px;
      padding:2.25rem 2rem;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;
      background:var(--bg);color:var(--muted);font-size:.88rem;
      transition:all .2s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;
    }
    .upload-area svg{width:34px;height:34px;stroke:var(--muted2);fill:none;stroke-width:1.5;margin-bottom:.2rem;transition:stroke .2s;}
    .upload-area:hover{border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber-dark);background:var(--amber-light);}
    .upload-area:hover svg{stroke:var(--amber-dark);}
    .upload-area input{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;cursor:pointer;}
    .upload-label{font-weight:600;}
    .upload-hint{font-size:.74rem;color:var(--muted2);}
    .upload-grid{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:.75rem;justify-content:flex-start;}
    .upload-thumb{position:relative;width:110px;height:110px;border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);}
    .upload-thumb img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;}
    .thumb-remove{position:absolute;top:6px;right:6px;border:none;border-radius:50%;width:26px;height:26px;background:rgba(15,23,42,.8);color:#fff;font-weight:900;cursor:pointer;line-height:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
    .upload-actions{display:flex;gap:.65rem;justify-content:flex-start;margin-top:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .upload-link{
      padding:.45rem .8rem;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border-mid);
      background:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text2);cursor:pointer;
      transition:.15s;
    }
    .upload-link:hover{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--blue);}
    .upload-link.danger{border-color:var(--red);color:var(--red);}

    /* submit */
    .submit-btn{
      width:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:9px;
      padding:1.1rem;margin-top:.65rem;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--amber),var(--orange));
      color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:var(--r-lg);
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:.98rem;
      cursor:pointer;transition:all .22s;
      box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(234,88,12,.34);position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .submit-btn svg{width:19px;height:19px;stroke:#fff;fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .submit-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 34px rgba(234,88,12,.44);}
    .submit-btn:active{transform:translateY(0);}
    .submit-btn::after{
      content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.18),transparent);
      transform:translateX(-100%);transition:transform .55s;
    }
    .submit-btn:hover::after{transform:translateX(100%);}

    /* ── MODALS / OVERLAYS ── */
    .overlay{
      display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;
      background:rgba(233,243,255,.95);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      z-index:500;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      flex-direction:column;text-align:center;padding:2rem;
    }
    .overlay.show{display:flex;animation:fadeIn .25s ease;}
    @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}

    /* success overlay */
    .success-ring{
      width:90px;height:90px;border-radius:50%;
      background:var(--green-light);border:2px solid var(--green-border);
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      margin-bottom:1.75rem;
      animation:scaleIn .4s .15s ease both;
      box-shadow:0 8px 36px rgba(5,150,105,.2);
    }
    @keyframes scaleIn{from{transform:scale(.5);opacity:0}to{transform:scale(1);opacity:1}}
    .success-ring svg{width:40px;height:40px;stroke:var(--green);fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .overlay h2{font-weight:900;font-size:2.1rem;letter-spacing:-1px;margin-bottom:.65rem;}
    .overlay p{color:var(--text2);max-width:370px;line-height:1.7;font-size:.93rem;}
    .rpt-id{
      margin-top:1.6rem;padding:1rem 2.5rem;
      background:var(--amber-light);border:1.5px solid var(--amber-border);border-radius:13px;
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.55rem;font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--amber-dark);
    }
    .ghost-btn{
      margin-top:1.75rem;padding:.75rem 2rem;
      background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);
      border-radius:var(--r-md);color:var(--text2);
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.88rem;cursor:pointer;
      transition:all .18s;
    }
    .ghost-btn:hover{border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber-dark);background:var(--amber-light);}

    /* panic setup modal */
    .modal-box{
      background:var(--surface);border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);
      border-top:3px solid var(--red);border-radius:var(--r-xl);
      padding:2.5rem;max-width:420px;width:100%;text-align:center;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl);
    }
    .modal-icon-wrap{
      width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:12px;
      background:var(--red-light);border:1.5px solid var(--red-border);
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 1.1rem;
    }
    .modal-icon-wrap svg{width:24px;height:24px;stroke:var(--red);fill:none;stroke-width:1.75;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .modal-box h3{font-weight:900;font-size:1.65rem;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:.55rem;}
    .modal-box p{color:var(--text2);font-size:.86rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.6rem;}
    .modal-box input{
      width:100%;background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border-mid);
      color:var(--text);padding:.9rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--r-md);
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.05rem;
      outline:none;text-align:center;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:1rem;transition:all .18s;
    }
    .modal-box input:focus{border-color:var(--red);box-shadow:0 0 0 3.5px rgba(220,38,38,.1);background:var(--surface);}
    .modal-save{
      width:100%;padding:.95rem;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#EF4444,#DC2626);
      color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:var(--r-md);
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:.97rem;cursor:pointer;
      box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(220,38,38,.3);transition:all .2s;
    }
    .modal-save:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(220,38,38,.4);}
    .modal-cancel{display:block;width:100%;padding:.55rem;margin-top:.6rem;background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;}

    /* panic sending overlay */
    #sendingOverlay{
      padding:1.25rem;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      text-align:center;
    }
    #sendingState{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      text-align:center;
      width:min(560px, 92vw);
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:2.2rem 2rem;
      border:1.5px solid var(--red-border);
      border-radius:20px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFFFFF 0%, #FFF8F8 100%);
      box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(220,38,38,.14);
    }
    .sending-ring{
      width:130px;height:130px;border-radius:50%;
      border:3px solid rgba(220,38,38,.15);border-top-color:var(--red);
      animation:spin .9s linear infinite;
      margin:0 auto 1.3rem;
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      position:relative;
    }
    .sending-ring::after{
      content:'';
      position:absolute;
      inset:-10px;
      border-radius:50%;
      border:1px solid rgba(220,38,38,.16);
    }
    @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
    .sending-ring svg{width:50px;height:50px;stroke:var(--red);fill:none;stroke-width:1.6;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .overlay h2.red{color:var(--red);}
    #sendingState h2.red{
      margin-bottom:.55rem;
      line-height:1.05;
      letter-spacing:-.8px;
      text-wrap:balance;
    }
    .sending-sub{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--text2);
      max-width:420px;
      line-height:1.55;
      font-size:1rem;
    }
    .overlay h2.green-h{color:var(--green);}
    .confirmed{
      display:none;
      flex-direction:column;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      text-align:center;
      width:min(560px, 92vw);
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:2.2rem 2rem;
      border:1.5px solid var(--green-border);
      border-radius:20px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFFFFF 0%, #F4FFF8 100%);
      box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(5,150,105,.14);
    }
    .confirmed.show{display:flex;}
    .confirm-ring{
      width:78px;height:78px;border-radius:50%;
      background:var(--green-light);border:2px solid var(--green-border);
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      margin-bottom:1.4rem;box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(5,150,105,.2);
    }
    .confirm-ring svg{width:34px;height:34px;stroke:var(--green);fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
    .sos-id-box{
      margin-top:1.4rem;padding:1rem 2.25rem;
      background:var(--red-light);border:1.5px solid var(--red-border);border-radius:12px;
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:1.7rem;font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--red);
    }
    .sos-id-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.58rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:5px;}
    .gps-note{margin-top:.85rem;font-size:.74rem;color:var(--muted);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}

    /* toast */
    .toast{
      position:fixed;bottom:1.75rem;right:1.75rem;z-index:999;
      display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;
      padding:.95rem 1.1rem;background:var(--surface);
      border:1px solid var(--border-mid);border-left:3px solid var(--green);
      border-radius:var(--r-md);box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl);max-width:300px;
      transform:translateX(calc(100% + 2rem));
      transition:transform .35s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);
    }
    .toast.show{transform:translateX(0);}
    .toast svg{width:15px;height:15px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;}
    .toast strong{display:block;font-weight:700;font-size:.83rem;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:1px;}
    .toast span{font-size:.76rem;color:var(--text2);}

    /* Highlight overrides */
    .card-title{font-weight:820;font-size:1.08rem;color:var(--blue);letter-spacing:-.25px;}
    .card-sub{color:var(--muted2);font-size:.82rem;}
    .field-note{color:var(--amber-deep);font-weight:600;}
    .mini-point strong{color:var(--blue);font-weight:850;font-size:.9rem;}
    .mini-point span{font-size:.82rem;}

    /* footer */
    .report-footer{
      margin:0;
      padding:2rem 1.35rem 2.2rem;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(29,78,216,.10), rgba(220,38,38,.08));
      border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .report-footer-inner{
      max-width:1100px;
      margin:0 auto;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.35fr 1fr;
      gap:1rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .rf-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.45rem;}
    .rf-logo{
      width:78px;height:68px;object-fit:contain;display:block;flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .rf-copy{margin-left:-10px;}
    .rf-name{font-weight:900;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.15;}
    .rf-sub{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:1.1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px;}
    .rf-text{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.65;margin-top:.38rem;max-width:340px;}
    .rf-col h4{
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.66rem;letter-spacing:1.1px;
      text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text2);margin:0 0 .45rem;
    }
    .rf-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:grid;gap:.34rem;}
    .rf-list li,.rf-link{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text2);text-decoration:none;}
    .rf-link:hover{text-decoration:underline;color:var(--blue);}
    .rf-bottom{
      max-width:1100px;
      margin:.95rem auto 0;
      padding-top:.75rem;
      border-top:1px dashed var(--border-mid);
      font-size:.73rem;color:var(--muted);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    @media(max-width:768px){
      .form-wrap{padding:2rem 1rem 3.5rem;}
      .form-head h1{font-size:2.2rem;}
      .card{padding:1.5rem;}
      .report-footer{padding:1.5rem 1rem 1.75rem}
      .report-footer-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1rem}
      .rf-text{max-width:none}
    }

    /* modern polish */
    body::before{
      content:'';
      position:fixed; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(148,163,184,.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148,163,184,.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 34px 34px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(0,0,0,.92), rgba(0,0,0,.30));
    }
    .header,.panic-strip,.form-wrap,.report-footer{position:relative;z-index:1}
    .header{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;
      align-items:center;
      gap:1rem;
      padding:1rem 1.5rem;
      background:rgba(243,247,255,.9);
      backdrop-filter:blur(18px);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);
      box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    }
    .brand{gap:.6rem}
    .panic-strip{
      margin: 1rem auto 0;
      width:min(1220px, calc(100% - 2rem));
      border:1px solid rgba(252,165,165,.34);
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 48px rgba(15,23,42,.10);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .panic-strip::after{
      content:'';
      position:absolute; inset:auto 8% -90px auto; width:260px; height:260px; border-radius:50%;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(220,38,38,.12), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .panic-eyebrow{font-size:1rem; letter-spacing:4px}
    .panic-btn{
      width:182px; height:182px;
      box-shadow:0 0 0 14px rgba(220,38,38,.08),0 0 0 30px rgba(220,38,38,.05),0 24px 48px rgba(220,38,38,.34);
    }
    .panic-sublabel{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.58);
      border:1px solid rgba(191,213,238,.58);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:1rem 1.2rem;
      max-width: 420px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .form-wrap{max-width:860px;padding-top:3.2rem}
    .form-head{margin-bottom:2.2rem}
    .form-head p{max-width:560px}
    .intro-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.35fr .95fr;
      gap:1rem;
      margin:1.35rem 0 0;
    }
    .intro-card{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      border:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);
      border-radius:20px;
      box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
      padding:1rem 1.05rem;
      backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    }
    .intro-title{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:.65rem;
      margin-bottom:.65rem;
    }
    .intro-icon{
      width:34px;
      height:34px;
      border-radius:11px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      background:var(--blue-light);
      border:1px solid var(--blue-border);
      color:var(--blue);
      flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .intro-icon svg{
      width:17px;
      height:17px;
      stroke:currentColor;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:1.8;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
    }
    .intro-title h3{
      font-size:.95rem;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:-.2px;
      color:var(--text);
    }
    .intro-title p{
      margin:2px 0 0;
      font-size:.74rem;
      line-height:1.5;
      color:var(--muted2);
      max-width:none;
    }
    .mini-points{
      display:grid;
      gap:.6rem;
    }
    .mini-point{
      display:flex;
      gap:.65rem;
      align-items:flex-start;
    }
    .mini-point strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:.78rem;
      color:var(--text2);
      margin-bottom:2px;
    }
    .mini-point span{
      display:block;
      font-size:.73rem;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.5;
    }
    .mini-dot{
      width:9px;
      height:9px;
      margin-top:.38rem;
      border-radius:999px;
      flex-shrink:0;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--amber),var(--orange));
      box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(250,204,21,.16);
    }
    .alert-strip{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
    }
    .card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248,251,255,.95), rgba(238,245,255,.92));
      border:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);
      border-radius:24px;
      box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
    }
    .card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 24px 48px rgba(15,23,42,.12)}
    .card-head{margin-bottom:1.35rem}
    .card-icon{
      width:52px; height:52px; border-radius:16px;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.7);
    }
    .field label{font-size:.72rem; letter-spacing:1px}
    input,select,textarea{
      border-radius:14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.82);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.72);
    }
    .etype-btn,.sev-btn,.upload-box,.gps-btn{
      border-radius:16px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
    }
    .etype-btn{align-items:flex-start;text-align:left;}
    .etype-copy{
      width:100%;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:3px;
      align-items:center;
      text-align:center;
    }
    .etype-copy strong{
      font-size:.83rem;
      font-weight:800;
      color:currentColor;
    }
    .etype-copy span{
      font-size:.67rem;
      line-height:1.35;
      color:var(--muted2);
      max-width:14ch;
    }
    .etype-btn:hover .etype-copy span,
    .etype-btn.sel .etype-copy span{color:currentColor;opacity:.78;}
    .severity-guide{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:.7rem;
      margin-top:.9rem;
    }
    .severity-note{
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:14px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      padding:.75rem .8rem;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow-xs);
    }
    .severity-note strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:.78rem;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }
    .severity-note span{
      display:block;
      font-size:.7rem;
      line-height:1.45;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .severity-note.low strong{color:var(--green);}
    .severity-note.med strong{color:var(--amber-dark);}
    .severity-note.high strong{color:var(--red);}
    .map-callout{
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-start;
      gap:.75rem;
      padding:.9rem 1rem;
      border:1px solid var(--blue-border);
      border-radius:16px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(219,234,254,.82),rgba(255,255,255,.78));
      color:var(--text2);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow-xs);
      margin-bottom:1rem;
    }
    .map-callout svg{
      width:18px;
      height:18px;
      stroke:currentColor;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:1.9;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
      flex-shrink:0;
      margin-top:1px;
    }
    .map-callout strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:.78rem;
      margin-bottom:2px;
      color:var(--text);
    }
    .map-callout span{
      display:block;
      font-size:.73rem;
      line-height:1.5;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .submit-btn,.panic-number-pill{
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .report-shell{
      max-width:1280px;
      margin:0 auto;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:minmax(0, 1fr) 336px;
      gap:1.7rem;
      align-items:start;
    }
    .report-main{min-width:0;}
    .report-aside{
      position:sticky;
      top:96px;
      display:grid;
      gap:1rem;
      transform:translateX(6px);
    }
    .aside-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(248,251,255,.95),rgba(236,244,255,.92));
      border:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);
      border-radius:22px;
      box-shadow:0 18px 36px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
      padding:1.15rem 1.1rem;
    }
    .aside-kicker{
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
      font-size:.6rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:2px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--red);
      margin-bottom:.8rem;
    }
    .aside-card h3{
      font-size:1rem;
      font-weight:800;
      color:var(--text);
      margin-bottom:.3rem;
      letter-spacing:-.2px;
    }
    .aside-card p{
      font-size:.84rem;
      line-height:1.65;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .step-links{
      display:grid;
      gap:.55rem;
      margin-top:.95rem;
    }
    .step-link{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:.75rem;
      padding:.72rem .85rem;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.65);
      text-decoration:none;
      transition:transform .18s ease,border-color .18s ease,background .18s ease;
    }
    .step-link:hover{
      transform:translateX(2px);
      border-color:var(--amber-border);
      background:var(--amber-light);
    }
    .step-link strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:.8rem;
      color:var(--text2);
    }
    .step-link span{
      display:block;
      font-size:.68rem;
      color:var(--muted2);
      margin-top:2px;
    }
    .step-no{
      width:34px;
      height:34px;
      border-radius:10px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      flex-shrink:0;
      background:var(--surface);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
      font-size:.72rem;
      font-weight:700;
      color:var(--amber-dark);
    }
    .tip-list{
      display:grid;
      gap:.75rem;
      margin-top:.95rem;
    }
    .tip-item{
      display:flex;
      gap:.7rem;
      align-items:flex-start;
    }
    .tip-icon{
      width:30px;
      height:30px;
      border-radius:10px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      flex-shrink:0;
      background:var(--blue-light);
      border:1px solid var(--blue-border);
      color:var(--blue);
    }
    .tip-icon svg{
      width:15px;
      height:15px;
      stroke:currentColor;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:1.8;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
    }
    .tip-copy strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:.8rem;
      color:var(--text);
      margin-bottom:2px;
    }
    .tip-copy span{
      display:block;
      font-size:.74rem;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .action-strip{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:.65rem;
      margin-top:1.2rem;
      justify-content:center;
      align-items:center;
      width:100%;
    }
    .action-chip{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:.48rem .78rem;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid var(--border-mid);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      color:var(--text2);
      font-size:.74rem;
      font-weight:700;
      text-decoration:none;
      transition:transform .18s ease,border-color .18s ease,background .18s ease,color .18s ease;
    }
    .action-chip:hover{
      transform:translateY(-1px);
      border-color:var(--amber-border);
      background:var(--amber-light);
      color:var(--amber-deep);
    }
    .action-chip svg{
      width:14px;
      height:14px;
      stroke:currentColor;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:1.8;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
    }
    .card-stack{
      display:grid;
      gap:1.2rem;
    }
    .card-topline{
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-start;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:1rem;
      margin-bottom:1rem;
    }
    .step-badge{
      flex-shrink:0;
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:.34rem .66rem;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
      font-size:.62rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:1px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .card-sub{max-width:44ch;line-height:1.55;color:var(--muted2);font-size:.82rem;}
    .field-note{
      margin-top:.45rem;
      font-size:.78rem;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:var(--amber-deep);
      font-weight:600;
    }
    .gps-meta{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:.6rem;
      margin:-.15rem 0 1rem;
    }
    .gps-meta-pill{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:.4rem .72rem;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      font-size:.72rem;
      font-weight:700;
      color:var(--text2);
    }
    .gps-meta-pill svg{
      width:13px;
      height:13px;
      stroke:currentColor;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:1.8;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
    }
    .submit-panel{
      margin-top:.25rem;
      padding:1.15rem;
      border-radius:22px;
      border:1px solid rgba(191,214,245,.9);
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.9),rgba(238,245,255,.92));
      box-shadow:0 18px 36px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
    }
    .submit-copy{
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-start;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:1rem;
      margin-bottom:.95rem;
    }
    .submit-copy h3{
      font-size:1rem;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:-.2px;
      color:var(--text);
      margin-bottom:.2rem;
    }
    .submit-copy p{
      font-size:.8rem;
      line-height:1.55;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:48ch;
    }
    .required-pill{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:.44rem .72rem;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:var(--amber-light);
      border:1px solid var(--amber-border);
      color:var(--amber-deep);
      font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
      font-size:.64rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:1px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }
    .required-pill svg{
      width:13px;
      height:13px;
      stroke:currentColor;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:1.8;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
    }
    .report-footer{
      margin-top:1rem;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(29,78,216,.12), rgba(220,38,38,.08));
    }
    @media(min-width:1024px){
      .panic-strip{
        width:min(1280px, calc(100% - 2.4rem));
        padding:2.7rem 2.2rem 3rem;
      }
      .form-wrap{
        max-width:1280px;
        padding:3.35rem 1.6rem 5rem;
      }
      .report-shell{
        grid-template-columns:minmax(0, 1.1fr) 360px;
        gap:2rem;
      }
      .report-main{
        max-width:880px;
      }
      .report-aside{
        top:104px;
        gap:1.15rem;
        transform:translateX(10px);
      }
      .aside-card{
        padding:1.2rem 1.15rem;
        border-radius:24px;
        box-shadow:0 22px 42px rgba(15,23,42,.09);
      }
      .aside-card:first-child{
        position:relative;
        overflow:hidden;
      }
      .aside-card:first-child::before{
        content:'';
        position:absolute;
        inset:0 0 auto 0;
        height:4px;
        background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue),var(--amber),var(--red));
        opacity:.9;
      }
      .step-links{
        gap:.7rem;
      }
      .step-link{
        padding:.8rem .9rem;
      }
      .intro-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1.2fr .88fr;
        gap:1.15rem;
      }
      .intro-card{
        padding:1.08rem 1.12rem;
      }
      .action-strip{
        max-width:420px;
        margin:1.2rem auto 0;
      }
      .alert-strip{
        padding:1.15rem 1.3rem;
      }
      .card-stack{
        gap:1.35rem;
      }
      .card{
        padding:2.1rem;
      }
      .card-topline{
        margin-bottom:1.2rem;
      }
      .etype-grid{
        gap:1rem;
      }
      .etype-btn{
        min-height:138px;
      }
      .gps-map-frame{
        height:250px;
      }
      .submit-panel{
        padding:1.2rem 1.25rem;
      }
    }
    @media(max-width:768px){
      .intro-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .severity-guide{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .report-shell{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
        gap:1rem;
      }
      .report-aside{
        position:static;
        order:1;
        transform:none;
        margin-top:.25rem;
      }
      .submit-copy{
        flex-direction:column;
      }
      .action-strip{
        width:100%;
        justify-content:center;
      }
      .action-chip{
        flex:1 1 220px;
        justify-content:center;
        min-height:44px;
      }
      .etype-btn,
      .sev-btn,
      .gps-btn,
      .submit-btn{
        min-height:52px;
      }
      .gps-meta{
        gap:.5rem;
      }
      .gps-meta-pill{
        width:100%;
        justify-content:flex-start;
      }
      .map-callout{
        padding:.85rem .9rem;
      }
      .step-links{
        grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      }
      .panic-strip{
        width:min(100%, calc(100% - 1rem));
        border-radius:24px;
      }
      .header{height:auto;min-height:64px;padding:.75rem 1rem;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
    .main-datetime{width:100%;white-space:normal;}
      .panic-sublabel{padding:.85rem 1rem}
    }
    @media(max-width:520px){
      .form-wrap{
        padding:1.5rem .85rem 3rem;
      }
      .intro-grid{
        margin-top:1rem;
      }
      .intro-card,
      .aside-card,
      .submit-panel{
        border-radius:18px;
        padding:.95rem;
      }
      .report-shell{
        gap:.85rem;
      }
      .card-topline{
        flex-direction:column;
        gap:.75rem;
      }
      .card{
        padding:1.2rem;
      }
      .card-head{
        gap:.85rem;
      }
      .card-icon{
        width:46px;
        height:46px;
      }
      .etype-grid{
        grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));
        gap:.7rem;
      }
      .etype-btn{
        min-height:132px;
        padding:1rem .55rem .9rem;
      }
      .etype-copy span{
        max-width:none;
      }
      .sev-row{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .sev-btn{
        justify-content:flex-start;
        padding:1rem;
      }
      .map-callout{
        gap:.6rem;
      }
      .step-links{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
      .step-link{
        padding:.78rem .85rem;
      }
      .panic-btn{
        width:164px;
        height:164px;
      }
      .action-chip{
        flex-basis:100%;
      }
      .main-datetime{padding:.68rem .85rem;gap:.7rem;}
      .main-datetime svg{width:20px;height:20px;}
      .clock-text{font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:.7px;}
      .date-text{font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.45px;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="header">
  <a class="brand" href="/about">
    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="SVS logo">
    <div class="brand-text">
      <div class="brand-name">SVS</div>
    <div class="brand-sub">Smart Verification System</div>
    </div>
  </a>
    <div class="header-right" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:.7rem;width:100%;">
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a class="nav-btn" href="/sos">SOS</a>
        <a class="nav-btn active" href="/report">Report</a>
        <a class="nav-btn" href="/about">About Us</a>
        <a class="nav-btn" href="/faq">FAQ</a>
      </div>
    <div class="main-datetime" id="reportTime">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6.75 3v2.25m10.5-2.25v2.25M3.75 9.75h16.5M4.5 5.25h15A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 21 6.75v12A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 19.5 20.25h-15A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 18.75v-12A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 5.25Z"/></svg>
      <div class="time-block"><span class="clock-text">--:--:--</span><span class="date-text">Loading...</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="form-wrap" id="report-form">
  <div class="report-shell">
    <div class="report-main">
  <div class="form-head">
    <div class="form-eyebrow">
      <!-- Heroicon: document-text -->
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z"/></svg>
      SVS Emergency Report System
    </div>
    <h1>Report an <em>Emergency</em></h1>
    <p>Your report will be received immediately by SVS dispatchers. Provide as much detail as possible for a faster response.</p>
    <div class="head-actions">
      <button class="chip-btn" type="button" onclick="alertQueued()">Offline Queue (<span id="pendingCount">0</span>)</button>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-grid">
      <div class="intro-card">
        <div class="intro-title">
          <div class="intro-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2.25"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Fastest way to file a usable report</h3>
            <p>Focus on what dispatch needs first, then add supporting detail.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-points">
          <div class="mini-point"><div class="mini-dot"></div><div><strong>Pin the exact location</strong><span>Use GPS on-site whenever it is safe. Barangay and landmark should match the real scene.</span></div></div>
          <div class="mini-point"><div class="mini-dot"></div><div><strong>Describe current risk</strong><span>Mention injuries, trapped people, spreading fire, rising water, blocked roads, or immediate hazards.</span></div></div>
          <div class="mini-point"><div class="mini-dot"></div><div><strong>Stay reachable after sending</strong><span>Dispatch may call back for quick verification while coordinating responders.</span></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-card">
        <div class="intro-title">
          <div class="intro-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.75 12h16.5M12 3.75v16.5"/><path d="M4.5 4.5h15v15h-15z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>What happens after you submit</h3>
            <p>The page is optimized for practical reporting, not long narratives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-points">
          <div class="mini-point"><div class="mini-dot"></div><div><strong>SVS receives the report instantly</strong><span>Dispatchers see your category, severity, location, and attached photo in real time.</span></div></div>
          <div class="mini-point"><div class="mini-dot"></div><div><strong>Location gets refreshed before send</strong><span>The system attempts one more GPS read on submission for better accuracy.</span></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="alert-strip">
    <!-- Heroicon: exclamation-triangle -->
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z"/></svg>
    <span><strong>For life-threatening emergencies, call 911 immediately.</strong><br>This form is for reporting incidents and requesting assistance through SVS.</span>
  </div>

  <div class="card-stack">
  <!-- STEP 01 -->
  <div class="card" id="step-reporter">
    <div class="card-topline">
      <div class="card-head">
      <div class="card-icon">
        <!-- Heroicon: user -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card-step">Step 01</div>
        <div class="card-title">Your Information</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Who is making this report?</div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-badge">Required</div>
    </div>
    <div class="row2">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Full Name *</label>
        <div class="input-wrap has-icon">
          <svg class="field-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z"/></svg>
          <input type="text" id="iName" placeholder="Juan dela Cruz" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field-note">Use the name responders or dispatchers can ask for during verification.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Contact Number *</label>
        <div class="input-wrap has-icon">
          <svg class="field-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.25 6.338c0 7.5 6.089 13.587 13.589 13.587l.682-.002a1.124 1.124 0 0 0 1.12-1.065l.254-3.223a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-.89-1.207l-2.98-.67a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.264.597l-.75 1.5a11.775 11.775 0 0 1-4.955-4.955l1.5-.75a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 .597-1.264l-.67-2.98a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.207-.89l-3.223.254a1.124 1.124 0 0 0-1.065 1.12L2.25 6.338Z"/></svg>
          <input type="tel" id="iContact" placeholder="+63 917 123 4567" inputmode="tel" autocomplete="tel" maxlength="16" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field-note">Use an active PH mobile number so dispatchers can call or text back immediately.</div>
        <div class="sos-save-row">
          <label for="iPanicContact">SOS number (for one-tap panic):</label>
          <input type="tel" id="iPanicContact" placeholder="+63 9XX XXX XXXX" inputmode="tel" maxlength="16">
          <button type="button" onclick="savePanicNumber()">Save SOS</button>
          <span class="pill-status" id="panicSavedStatus"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 02 -->
  <div class="card" id="step-type">
    <div class="card-topline">
      <div class="card-head">
      <div class="card-icon">
        <!-- Heroicon: exclamation-circle -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008Z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card-step">Step 02</div>
        <div class="card-title">Type of Emergency</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Select the category that best describes the incident</div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-badge">Choose one</div>
    </div>
    <div class="etype-grid" id="typeGrid">
      <div class="etype-btn" onclick="selType(this,'Fire')">
        <div class="etype-icon">
          <!-- Heroicon: fire -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0 1 12 21 8.25 8.25 0 0 1 6.038 7.047 8.287 8.287 0 0 0 9 9.601a8.983 8.983 0 0 1 3.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 0 0 3 2.48Z"/><path d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 .495-7.468 5.99 5.99 0 0 0-1.925 3.547 5.975 5.975 0 0 1-2.133-1.001A3.75 3.75 0 0 0 12 18Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="etype-copy"><strong>Fire</strong><span>House, building, grass, or electrical fire</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="etype-btn" onclick="selType(this,'Flood')">
        <div class="etype-icon">
          <!-- Heroicon: cloud -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 1.332-7.257 3 3 0 0 0-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 0 0-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 0 0 2.25 15Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="etype-copy"><strong>Flood</strong><span>Rising water, overflow, or stranded areas</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="etype-btn" onclick="selType(this,'Medical')">
        <div class="etype-icon">
          <!-- Heroicon: heart -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11.645 20.91l-.007-.003-.022-.012a15.247 15.247 0 0 1-.383-.218 25.18 25.18 0 0 1-4.244-3.17C4.688 15.36 2.25 12.174 2.25 8.25 2.25 5.322 4.714 3 7.688 3A5.5 5.5 0 0 1 12 5.052 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 16.313 3c2.973 0 5.437 2.322 5.437 5.25 0 3.925-2.438 7.111-4.739 9.256a25.175 25.175 0 0 1-4.244 3.17 15.247 15.247 0 0 1-.383.219l-.022.012-.007.004-.003.001a.752.752 0 0 1-.704 0l-.003-.001Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="etype-copy"><strong>Medical</strong><span>Injury, illness, collapse, or urgent rescue</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="etype-btn" onclick="selType(this,'Accident')">
        <div class="etype-icon">
          <!-- Heroicon: truck -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 0 0-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 0 0-1.58-.86H14.25M8.25 18.75V3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h5.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="etype-copy"><strong>Accident</strong><span>Vehicle crash, impact, or road incident</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="etype-btn" onclick="selType(this,'Landslide')">
        <div class="etype-icon">
          <!-- Heroicon: chart-bar -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="etype-copy"><strong>Landslide</strong><span>Soil movement, collapse, or debris fall</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="etype-btn" onclick="selType(this,'Other')">
        <div class="etype-icon">
          <!-- Heroicon: ellipsis-horizontal-circle -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8.625 12a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Zm0 0h-.375M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="etype-copy"><strong>Other</strong><span>Use when no listed category fits the incident</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" id="iType">
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 03 -->
  <div class="card" id="step-severity">
    <div class="card-topline">
      <div class="card-head">
      <div class="card-icon">
        <!-- Heroicon: bolt -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="m3.75 13.5 10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card-step">Step 03</div>
        <div class="card-title">Severity Level</div>
        <div class="card-sub">How serious is the situation right now?</div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-badge">Priority</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sev-row" id="sevGrid">
      <button class="sev-btn low" type="button" onclick="selSev(this,'Low')">
        <!-- Heroicon: check-circle -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>Low
      </button>
      <button class="sev-btn med" type="button" onclick="selSev(this,'Medium')">
        <!-- Heroicon: exclamation-circle -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008Z"/></svg>Medium
      </button>
      <button class="sev-btn high" type="button" onclick="selSev(this,'High')">
        <!-- Heroicon: exclamation-triangle -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z"/></svg>High
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="severity-guide">
      <div class="severity-note low"><strong>Low</strong><span>Stable incident, no immediate life threat, responders can approach normally.</span></div>
      <div class="severity-note med"><strong>Medium</strong><span>Urgent situation with possible escalation or people needing prompt assistance.</span></div>
      <div class="severity-note high"><strong>High</strong><span>Immediate danger to life, active hazard, trapped victims, or rapidly worsening conditions.</span></div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" id="iSev">
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 04 -->
  <div class="card" id="step-location">
    <div class="card-topline">
      <div class="card-head">
      <div class="card-icon">
        <!-- Heroicon: map-pin -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z"/><path d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card-step">Step 04</div>
        <div class="card-title">Location</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Where is the emergency happening?</div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-badge">GPS first</div>
    </div>
    <button class="gps-btn" id="gpsBtn" type="button" onclick="detectGPS()">
      <!-- Heroicon: signal -->
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.348 14.651a3.75 3.75 0 0 1 0-5.303m5.304-.001a3.75 3.75 0 0 1 0 5.304m-7.425 2.122a6.75 6.75 0 0 1 0-9.546m9.546 0a6.75 6.75 0 0 1 0 9.546M5.106 18.894c-3.808-3.808-3.808-9.98 0-13.789m13.788 0c3.808 3.808 3.808 9.981 0 13.79M12 12h.008v.007H12V12Zm.375 0a.375.375 0 1 1-.75 0 .375.375 0 0 1 .75 0Z"/></svg>
      Auto-detect My Location (GPS)
    </button>
    <div class="gps-meta">
      <div class="gps-meta-pill">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2.25"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>
        Best used at the scene
      </div>
      <div class="gps-meta-pill">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.25 12.76c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.67 3.337l2.315.514a48.59 48.59 0 0 0 9.53 0l2.314-.514a3.417 3.417 0 0 0 2.671-3.337V9.24a3.417 3.417 0 0 0-2.67-3.337l-2.315-.514a48.591 48.591 0 0 0-9.53 0l-2.314.514A3.417 3.417 0 0 0 2.25 9.24v3.52Z"/><path d="M12 9v3.75"/></svg>
        Auto-fills nearby details when available
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="map-callout">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.25c-3.728 0-6.75 3.022-6.75 6.75 0 5.444 6.75 12.75 6.75 12.75S18.75 14.444 18.75 9c0-3.728-3.022-6.75-6.75-6.75Z"/><path d="M12 11.25a2.25 2.25 0 1 0 0-4.5 2.25 2.25 0 0 0 0 4.5Z"/></svg>
      <div>
        <strong>Use the map as a confirmation step</strong>
        <span>After GPS detection, check whether the pin matches the actual incident scene before submitting. If it looks off, update the barangay, landmark, and street fields manually.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gps-map-wrap" id="gpsMapWrap">
      <div class="gps-map-head">
        <span id="gpsMapLabel">Detected location</span>
        <a id="gpsMapLink" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open map</a>
      </div>
      <div class="gps-map-canvas">
        <iframe class="gps-map-frame" id="gpsMapFrame" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
        <div class="gps-map-view-toggle">
          <button class="gps-map-control" id="gpsMapViewToggle" type="button" disabled title="Switch between standard and satellite imagery">
            Show satellite image
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="gps-map-zoom" id="gpsMapZoomGroup">
          <button class="gps-map-control gps-map-control--compact" id="gpsMapZoomOut" type="button" aria-label="Zoom out" disabled>−</button>
          <span id="gpsMapZoomValue">16x</span>
          <button class="gps-map-control gps-map-control--compact" id="gpsMapZoomIn" type="button" aria-label="Zoom in" disabled>+</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input type="hidden" id="iGPS">
    <input type="hidden" id="iGPSAt">
    <input type="hidden" id="iGPSAcc">
    <div class="row2">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Barangay *</label>
        <div class="input-wrap has-icon">
          <svg class="field-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z"/></svg>
          <input type="text" id="iBarangay" placeholder="e.g. Barangay Rizal" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field-note">Keep this specific so responders can route the report to the correct area.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Nearest Landmark *</label>
        <div class="input-wrap has-icon">
          <svg class="field-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z"/><path d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z"/></svg>
          <input type="text" id="iLandmark" placeholder="e.g. Near Municipal Hall" required>
        </div>
        <div class="field-note">Use a building, crossing, school, bridge, or any place responders can spot quickly.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label>Street / Additional Details *</label>
      <div class="input-wrap has-icon">
        <svg class="field-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3.75 5.25h16.5m-16.5 4.5h16.5m-16.5 4.5h16.5m-16.5 4.5h16.5"/></svg>
        <input type="text" id="iStreet" placeholder="Street name or additional details" required>
      </div>
      <div class="field-note">Include purok, road direction, blocked access, or any detail that helps the team approach safely.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 05 -->
  <div class="card" id="step-details">
    <div class="card-topline">
      <div class="card-head">
      <div class="card-icon">
        <!-- Heroicon: pencil-square -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16.862 4.487 18.55 2.8a1.875 1.875 0 1 1 2.652 2.652L10.582 16.07a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-1.897 1.13L6 18l.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 1.13-1.897l8.932-8.931Zm0 0L19.5 7.125M18 14v4.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 15.75 21H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 18.75V8.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 5.25 6H10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card-step">Step 05</div>
        <div class="card-title">Incident Details</div>
        <div class="card-sub">Describe the situation and attach a photo if possible</div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-badge">Context</div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label>Key conditions (optional)</label>
      <div class="tag-grid" id="tagGrid">
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="people_trapped" onclick="toggleTag('people_trapped')">People trapped</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="injured" onclick="toggleTag('injured')">Injured</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="road_blocked" onclick="toggleTag('road_blocked')">Road blocked</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="power_out" onclick="toggleTag('power_out')">Power out</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="rising_water" onclick="toggleTag('rising_water')">Rising water</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="fire_spreading" onclick="toggleTag('fire_spreading')">Fire spreading</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="hazmat" onclick="toggleTag('hazmat')">Chemical / HazMat</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="structure_damage" onclick="toggleTag('structure_damage')">Structural damage</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="blocked_access" onclick="toggleTag('blocked_access')">Access blocked</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="missing_persons" onclick="toggleTag('missing_persons')">Missing persons</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="medical_needed" onclick="toggleTag('medical_needed')">Medical needed</button>
        <button type="button" class="tag-chip" data-tag="evac_needed" onclick="toggleTag('evac_needed')">Evac needed</button>
      </div>
      <div class="field-note">Check any that apply to help dispatch triage faster.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label>Description (optional)</label>
      <textarea id="iDesc" placeholder="Describe what is happening. Include: number of people affected, current situation, any danger present…"></textarea>
      <div class="field-note">Optional but helpful: injuries, trapped people, hazards, flooding depth, fire spread, or anything changing fast.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label>Attestation *</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <label class="attest-check">
          <input type="checkbox" id="iAttest">
          <span>I confirm this report is truthful and not a prank.</span>
        </label>
        <div class="field-note">False reports may delay real emergencies and can be subject to penalties.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label>Upload Photo (Optional)</label>
      <div class="upload-area" id="uploadArea">
        <input id="uploadFile" type="file" accept="image/*" onchange="handlePhoto(this)">
        <!-- Heroicon: camera -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6.827 6.175A2.31 2.31 0 0 1 5.186 7.23c-.38.054-.757.112-1.134.175C2.999 7.58 2.25 8.507 2.25 9.574V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21.75 18V9.574c0-1.067-.75-1.994-1.802-2.169a47.865 47.865 0 0 0-1.134-.175 2.31 2.31 0 0 1-1.64-1.055l-.822-1.316a2.192 2.192 0 0 0-1.736-1.039 48.774 48.774 0 0 0-5.232 0 2.192 2.192 0 0 0-1.736 1.039l-.821 1.316Z"/><path d="M16.5 12.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 1-9 0 4.5 4.5 0 0 1 9 0ZM18.75 10.5h.008v.008h-.008V10.5Z"/></svg>
        <div class="upload-label">Click or drag to upload a photo</div>
        <div class="upload-hint">JPG, PNG — up to 10 MB</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field-note">A clear photo helps dispatchers verify the situation faster, but it should never delay reporting.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="submit-panel">
    <div class="submit-copy">
      <div>
        <h3>Ready to send the report?</h3>
        <p>Check that your contact number, severity, and location are correct. The system will try to refresh GPS again before final submission.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="required-pill">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>
        Required fields only
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="submit-btn" type="button" onclick="submitReport()">
      <!-- Heroicon: paper-airplane -->
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 12 3.269 3.125A59.769 59.769 0 0 1 21.485 12 59.768 59.768 0 0 1 3.27 20.875L5.999 12Zm0 0h7.5"/></svg>
      Submit Emergency Report
    </button>
  </div>
  </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="report-aside" aria-label="Reporting help">
      <div class="aside-card">
        <div class="aside-kicker">Quick Guide</div>
        <h3>Complete the report in order</h3>
        <p>Follow the five sections below. The most important details are your callback number, exact location, and a short description of what is happening now.</p>
        <div class="step-links">
          <a class="step-link" href="#step-reporter"><div><strong>Reporter details</strong><span>Name and contact number</span></div><div class="step-no">01</div></a>
          <a class="step-link" href="#step-type"><div><strong>Emergency type</strong><span>Choose the closest match</span></div><div class="step-no">02</div></a>
          <a class="step-link" href="#step-severity"><div><strong>Severity</strong><span>Tell dispatch how urgent it is</span></div><div class="step-no">03</div></a>
          <a class="step-link" href="#step-location"><div><strong>Location</strong><span>GPS, barangay, landmark, street</span></div><div class="step-no">04</div></a>
          <a class="step-link" href="#step-details"><div><strong>Incident details</strong><span>Description and optional photo</span></div><div class="step-no">05</div></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card">
        <div class="aside-kicker">Best Practice</div>
        <h3>What helps responders most</h3>
        <div class="tip-list">
          <div class="tip-item">
            <div class="tip-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z"/><path d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z"/></svg></div>
            <div class="tip-copy"><strong>Pin the exact scene</strong><span>Use GPS while you are physically near the emergency if it is safe to do so.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-item">
            <div class="tip-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7.5 12h9m-9 3.75h5.25M6.75 3h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 19.5 5.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 17.25 21H6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 18.75V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6.75 3Z"/></svg></div>
            <div class="tip-copy"><strong>Keep the description short and factual</strong><span>State what happened, who is affected, and immediate risks instead of long background details.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-item">
            <div class="tip-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.25 6.338c0 7.5 6.089 13.587 13.589 13.587l.682-.002a1.124 1.124 0 0 0 1.12-1.065l.254-3.223a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-.89-1.207l-2.98-.67a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.264.597l-.75 1.5a11.775 11.775 0 0 1-4.955-4.955l1.5-.75a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 .597-1.264l-.67-2.98a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.207-.89l-3.223.254a1.124 1.124 0 0 0-1.065 1.12L2.25 6.338Z"/></svg></div>
            <div class="tip-copy"><strong>Stay reachable after submitting</strong><span>Dispatchers may verify details before sending or while coordinating responders.</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</div>

